表格通讯管理的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('CommunicationInfo')
and type = 'U')
drop table CommunicationInfo
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: CommunicationInfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table CommunicationInfo (
ID int identity(1,1),
MachineNo varchar(20) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
CollectorNo varchar(20) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
APName varchar(20) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
APAddr varchar(20) null,
IPAddr varchar(20) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
Port int not null,
NetGate varchar(20) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
CommStatus varchar(20) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
Remark varchar(200) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
constraint PK_COMMUNICATIONINFO primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
go
